::Zardus/The Iron Fist::

Various cameras hidden in the cealing and walls were all monitoring Orchestra, reporting to Zardus.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus recieves Vamprah's comm, heading down to hers and Wheeljack's location. He frowns, the Iron Fist's report on what Orchestra was asking for reaching him in a transmission from the Iron Fist.

He speeds up his walk, getting closer to where Orchestra was.
